3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses machine learning techniques to predict depth maps and complete 3D object point clouds. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses AI techniques to infer 3D point clouds from single images. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with generating 3D point clouds, which is a common topic in computer graphics.
